      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 25.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>可以為天下母。吾不知其名，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>I do not know its name, and I give it the designation of the Dao (the Way or Course).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
