      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 25.5 - 老子 25.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>字之曰道，強為之名曰大。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Making an effort (further) to give it a name I call it The Great. Great, it passes on (in constant flow).</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
