      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 25.13 - 老子 25.14</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>王亦大。域中有四大，而王居其一焉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the universe there are four that are great, and the (sage) king is one of them. Man takes his law from the Earth;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
